**README.md**

# To-Do List App

This is a simple to-do list application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. It helps users organize their tasks and manage their daily activities efficiently.

## Features

- Add tasks with a title and optional description
- Mark tasks as complete
- Delete tasks
- Filter tasks by status (all, active, completed)
- Save tasks locally in the browser

## Usage

1. Clone the repository to your local machine:

   ```
   git clone https://github.com/Fabiyanoor/todo-list.git
   ```

2. Open `index.html` in your preferred web browser.

3. To add a new task, type the task title in the input field and press Enter. You can also add an optional description for the task.

4. To mark a task as complete, click on the checkbox next to the task.

5. To delete a task, click on the delete icon (trash can) next to the task.

6. Use the filter buttons at the bottom to view all tasks, only active tasks, or only completed tasks.

7. Your tasks will be saved locally in the browser, so you can revisit the page later and find your tasks intact.

